Package harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib

Enum TGameStatus

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<TGameStatus>
harrygpotter.tombola.tombolalib.TGameStatus
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TGameStatus>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum TGameStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<TGameStatus>
Enum class used by TGame to maintain the status of the game, thus allowing or disabling possible game operations in each status.
Since:
1.8
Version:
1.1
Author:
Harry G. Potter harry.g.potter@gmail.com
See Also:
TGame, TGameResultCode

  • Enum Constant Summary

    Enum Constants 
    Enum Constant Description
    BUSY
    A number has been extracted and the TGame object is busy because checks are performed on all playing cards and game status must be properly update.
    ENDED
    Tombola game is over, even the last 'tombolino' award has been assigned, you have just to say hello to your playing friends or to start a new match!
    INITIALIZING
    The tombola match is still not started and mandatory elements (the 'sacchetto', the playing cards, the tombola billboard) are going to be prepared.
    PLAYING
    Game is ongoing, the first number has been extracted and there are still numbers in the ballot box to be extracted and prizes available to be won.
    READY
    Tombola match has still not been started, but all mandatory elements of the game have been correctly prepared and everything is read to start and extract the first number.
    RESOLVING
    A number has been extracted, checks have been performed and MORE THAN ONE CARD has matched the proper amount of hits to be candidate to the next available award.

  • Enum Constant Details

    • INITIALIZING

      public static final TGameStatus INITIALIZING
      The tombola match is still not started and mandatory elements (the 'sacchetto', the playing cards, the tombola billboard) are going to be prepared.

    • READY

      public static final TGameStatus READY
      Tombola match has still not been started, but all mandatory elements of the game have been correctly prepared and everything is read to start and extract the first number.

    • PLAYING

      public static final TGameStatus PLAYING
      Game is ongoing, the first number has been extracted and there are still numbers in the ballot box to be extracted and prizes available to be won.

    • BUSY

      public static final TGameStatus BUSY
      A number has been extracted and the TGame object is busy because checks are performed on all playing cards and game status must be properly update.

    • RESOLVING

      public static final TGameStatus RESOLVING
      A number has been extracted, checks have been performed and MORE THAN ONE CARD has matched the proper amount of hits to be candidate to the next available award. The TombolaLib user must decide the winner (or the winners) thus resolving the conflict before proceed with next number extraction

    • ENDED

      public static final TGameStatus ENDED
      Tombola game is over, even the last 'tombolino' award has been assigned, you have just to say hello to your playing friends or to start a new match!
